  "notes": "Provides a focused HTTP/1.1 baseline for loopback and local-integration scenarios. The current slice supports createServer(), request(), and get() on top of the runtime's minimal node:net transport, with EventEmitter-backed request/response objects, Content-Length framing, and connection-close completion semantics. Chunked transfer encoding, keep-alive/agents, upgrade handling, HTTPS URLs, and broader streaming/header edge cases are not implemented yet.",
  "apis": [
